<cb:div type="zangwai-notes">
<head>方廣錩 校注</head>
<p>
<note n="0373001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0373001">「俱」，底本作「具」，據文意改。</note>
<note n="0373002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0373002">「於」，底本殘，據文意補。</note>
<note n="0374001" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0374001">「鉞」，底本作「越」，據文意改。</note>
<note n="0374002" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0374002">「智」，疑作「持」或「捧」。</note>
